1. Admin defines ROUTES (with ordered stops + direction)

2. System defines TIME SLOTS (timetable per route)

3. Staff/Driver:
   → books a slot (creates Trip)
   → gets reminder
   → clicks START → trip becomes running

4. User:
   → selects stops OR route
   → sees matching trips (time + direction)
   → selects bus → joins room → live tracking




   
   PS H:\bus\bus\backend> npx nodemon server.js # backend